# 8. 自分達の手で

Ichika: Pardon us!
Free Cluster Member A: Oh, Leo/need's here!
Honami: We came to congratulate all of you... Would it be alright if we came in?
Free Cluster Member B: Of course! Come in, come in!
Honami: Thank you again for allowing us to open for you. This ended up being an invaluable experience.
Free Cluster Member C: No, we should be the ones thanking you. I mean, the way you got that crowd going.
Free Cluster Member A: Yeah, they were bouncing off the walls. That ended up being a huge boost for us.
Ichika: No, we just...
Naruse: Don't be so modest. You succeeded in drawing everyone into your world, Leo/need.
Naruse: You put on an outstanding performance.
Saki: Ms. Naruse...!
Shiho: Thank you very much. We really appreciate you saying that.
Shiho: But after seeing your performance, we know we still have an incredibly long way to go.
Saki: Yes, you were all absolutely, amazingly awesome...!
Naruse: ♪————!
Shiho: You became one with everybody in the arena. So much so that we could feel the entire place shaking from just off the stage.
Shiho: I hope we can put on a show like that someday.
Shiho: We plan on doing our best moving forward to learn how to really move everyone's hearts.
Naruse: *Nod* Next time we share a stage, it won't be as opener and headliner. Let's face off as rivals.
Naruse: I'll definitely be looking forward to that day.
Shiho: Us too!
Saki: Hehe. My heart's still racing.
Ichika: Mine too. I wasn't sure if we'd be able to get everybody going, but I'm so happy we did.
Shiho: Yeah. That was so much fun...
Shiho: (I can still feel it...)
Shiho: (The way the crowd's cheers and applause made the entire place shake.)
Shiho: (They took the energy we put into our sound and responded...)
Honami: Shiho...?
Shiho: Huh?
Honami: Is everything okay? You seemed out of it for a second.
Shiho: Oh, no. I'm fine.
Shiho: I was just going back over what happened while we were on stage.
Shiho: I've always wanted to move people's hearts with our music, but...
Shiho: After standing on that stage today and basking in the energy the crowd produced...
Shiho: I feel like I got a taste of what it's like for my dream to come true.
Ichika: Shiho...
Shiho: I want to stand there again someday, as the headliners.
Shiho: I want us to create that moment through our own power.
Shiho: The four of us. Together.
Honami, Ichika & Saki: Yeah...!
Ichika: Then, we'll need to get a lot better.
Saki: And write even more amazing songs!
Honami: Let's rest tonight, and jump right back into it tomorrow!
Women: How awesome was that show?!
Women: Super awesome! Free Cluster's seriously the best band in the world! I'm a fan for life!
Saki: (Oh, they must've been in the crowd today...)
Women: Leo/need was also really good! I've been following them for a little while, but they really feel like pros now!
Saki: ...!
Women: I know, right?! But...
Women: I'm also a little sad. I mean, the more famous they get, the further away they're going to fly.
Women: Yeah, I know what you mean. I am happy that more people know about them now, but...
Saki: Oh...
Shiho: Saki...? What are you spacing out for?
Saki: Oh, sorry...! I was just thinking how fun today's show was!
Shiho: You were the one who said we should throw an after-party. We're gonna leave you behind if you keep dawdling.
Saki: What?! No, wait! Don't leave me!
